ygData.messageBody:
I also did not recieve a key. When I looked into it I noticed it said
player of "mid-level" characters. Since my highest is 17 now, I think that
is why I was left out. Not sure if this matters to you, but since the keys
were sent out starting May 31, you might have missed it because of that.

Just a note, all keys not used go bad July 2, so if you have one you might
want to use it or let us know about it pretty soon. Would hate to see all
those keys go bad.
